content.text: This paper introduces the AutoTeX pipeline that converts complex documents into structured JSON outputs for downstream agents. The system leverages AI techniques and strict schema validation [1].

inlines.text: This paper introduces the AutoTeX pipeline that converts complex documents into structured JSON outputs for downstream agents. The system leverages AI techniques and strict schema validation [1].

content.text: Traditional document digitization workflows rely on manual formatting. AutoTeX automates this process by combining deterministic parsing with LLM-based inference.
